Linux-Quiz
==========

A Quiz for Linux controlled with Playstations Buzz! Controllers

Website: http://www.pascals-koenigreich.de/2012/02/quiz-spiel-textversion-10.html

Prerequisites:
	- You must have libusb-1.0 installed

The Question CSV File is from quiz-fabrik.de: http://www.quiz-fabrik.de/media/quiz-fragen.csv
